    "• Use bacteriostatic water (BW) as diluent for extended shelf life\n• Reconstituted peptides should be stored at 2–8°C\n• Draw air = inject volume of air before drawing peptide": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Bakteriostatisches Wasser (BW) als Verdünner für längere Haltbarkeit\n• Rekonstituierte Peptide bei 2–8°C lagern\n• Luft ziehen = gleiches Luftvolumen spritzen, bevor du das Peptid ziehst"
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Usa agua bacteriostática (BW) como diluyente para mayor vida útil\n• Los péptidos reconstituidos deben guardarse a 2–8 °C\n• Aire = inyecta el mismo volumen de aire antes de aspirar el péptido"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Eau bactériostatique (BW) comme diluant pour une meilleure conservation\n• Peptides reconstitués à conserver entre 2–8 °C\n• Air = injecter le même volume d’air avant d’aspirer le peptide"
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Acqua batteriostatica (BW) come diluente per una conservazione migliore\n• Peptidi ricostituiti conservare a 2–8 °C\n• Aria = iniettare lo stesso volume d’aria prima di aspirare il peptide"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Use bacteriostatic water (BW) as diluent for extended shelf life\n• Reconstituted peptides should be stored at 2–8°C\n• Draw air = inject volume of air before drawing peptide"
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Use bacteriostatic water (BW) as diluent for extended shelf life\n• Reconstituted peptides should be stored at 2–8°C\n• Draw air = inject volume of air before drawing peptide"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Use bacteriostatic water (BW) as diluent for extended shelf life\n• Reconstituted peptides should be stored at 2–8°C\n• Draw air = inject volume of air before drawing peptide"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "• Use bacteriostatic water (BW) as diluent for extended shelf life\n• Reconstituted peptides should be stored at 2–8°C\n• Draw air = inject volume of air before drawing peptide"
